cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or data, please cite as below."
title: "sparc-halo-shell-reality: Statistical organization of localized residual structure in SPARC rotation curves (Paper II companion)"
abstract: >-
  Companion software and data products for Paper II of the halo_shells series.
  Contains the manuscript source, the per-shell analysis pipeline, perturbation
  and null-test scripts, anti-warp clean subsample fits, Einasto and gNFW
  backbone-family control fits, and all derived per-galaxy and per-shell CSVs
  for the 102-galaxy SPARC T=2-9 sample.
type: software
