license: MIT
keywords:
  - galaxy rotation curves
  - SPARC catalog
  - dark matter halos
  - localized residual structure
  - shell-bearing galaxies
  - Burkert profile
  - Einasto profile
  - generalized NFW profile
  - astrostatistics
  - Bayesian information criterion
references:
